race.description: Book Your Xmas Party Sunday 21st Dec Hcp
race.comment: KNOWITALL FRANK (3) is third-up seeking the hat-trick, and it was a big effort at Inverell last time from the wide gate. Will have to do it the hard way again, but presents fitter and can win again with average luck. RESOLUTE LADY (10) threatened her twice before delivering a 55 win at Kilcoy. Has an awkward barrier but has a 2kg claim today and is a chance to repeat the dose. UPSTART LOVER (14) led and won her Maiden comfortably at Toowoomba. Draws inside today, and she looks to have turned the corner. She has winning claims. LA PITTRICE (7) has been racing in stronger and is busting to win. She'll get every chance from the rails gate.
